{"comments":"Pure PureScript implementation of Keccak-256 (Ethereum's hash).\n\nKeccak-256 is the hash function used by Ethereum for:\n- Address derivation from public keys\n- EIP-712 typed data signing (x402 protocol)\n- Transaction and block hashing\n\n## Why Keccak-256?\n\nThe x402 protocol uses EIP-712 structured data hashing, which requires\nKeccak-256. This enables Hydrogen attestations to be compatible with\nEthereum wallets and on-chain verification.\n\n## Algorithm Overview\n\nKeccak uses a sponge construction:\n1. State: 5×5 array of 64-bit lanes (1600 bits total)\n2. Rate: 1088 bits (136 bytes) for Keccak-256\n3. Capacity: 512 bits\n4. 24 rounds of permutation (θ, ρ, π, χ, ι)\n5. Squeeze 256 bits of output\n\n## 64-bit Arithmetic\n\nPureScript Int is 32-bit, so we represent 64-bit lanes as pairs of Ints\n(high word, low word). This is slower but pure and portable.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Attestation","Keccak256"],"Keccak256Hash"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[74,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/Keccak256.purs","start":[74,1]},"title":"eqKeccak256Hash"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Attestation","Keccak256"],"Keccak256Hash"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[75,54],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/Keccak256.purs","start":[75,1]},"title":"ordKeccak256Hash"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Attestation","Keccak256"],"Keccak256Hash"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[78,25],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/Keccak256.purs","start":[77,1]},"title":"showKeccak256Hash"}],"comments":"A Keccak-256 hash — 256 bits represented as eight 32-bit words.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[72,50],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/Keccak256.purs","start":[72,1]},"title":"Keccak256Hash"},{"children":[],"comments":"Compute Keccak-256 hash of a string (ASCII bytes)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Attestation","Keccak256"],"Keccak256Hash"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[450,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/Keccak256.purs","start":[450,1]},"title":"keccak256"},{"children":[],"comments":"Compute Keccak-256 hash of byte array\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Attestation","Keccak256"],"Keccak256Hash"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[395,45],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Attestation/Keccak256.purs","start":[395,1]},"title":"keccak256Bytes"},{"children":[],"comments":"Comp